{"tid":61424,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚認真] 入黎將歌詞中譯英","createTime":"2016-12-31T08:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T12:10:24.000Z","uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d37e87c9359f2b2fa540c6a9035b9f44f9aa650","tid":61424,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:35:48.000Z","msg":"淨係譯左一首個框先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\n我想啲外國同學睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宣揚下廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲位跟唔到grammar(不過英文歌grammar鬆手嘅)又或者用詞不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手執下啦<br />\n我想可以啱音唱添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe past, the present, are the things we can't hold<br />\nFallen leaves are buried in soil<br />\nThe start and the end never have been changed<br />\nThe love of my life's gone so far away<br />\n<br />\nLove and hatred surging<br />\nIt's my fate, I couldn't run away<br />\nWith love, why can't we stay together <br />\nI guess it's what they call love<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'Goodbye' from a lover is cruel <br />\nQuietly sitting alone facing the world<br />\nAlthough the roses wilted,  it will relive <br />\nI glimpse the love of my life above(in?) the sky <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">一生所愛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac57d9837dcad121357d3dc329e2a6cb434791e","tid":61424,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"if you dont think it's stupid ,holding hand by the famous crazy guy"},{"pid":"770bffe6b09c6b2382ccb3b860108ed8726c8d9a","tid":61424,"uid"